<h4><a name="cat2-q1"></a>Is my donation secure?</h4>
<p>All of your information is captured and processed with industry standard security measures in place as established by
  the credit card industry. All data that is transmitted between your browser and our servers is encrypted with the
  industry standard SSL secure socket layer protection. Additionally, Kiindly transactions are processed through Stripe,
  a PCI compliant level 1 service provider, the highest level of security credential for credit card processing.
  <a href="http://usa.visa.com/download/merchants/cisp-list-of-pcidss-compliant-service-providers.pdf" target="_blank">Read
    More on Visa.com &raquo;</a>.</p>


